| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1304 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5fd6e1aa-02d4-5ae3-8674-7bc191015f3b"
